1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:22,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

2
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

3
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

4
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

5
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

6
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

7
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

8
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

9
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

10
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

11
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

12
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

13
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

14
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

15
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

16
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

17
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

18
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

19
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

20
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

21
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

22
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

23
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

24
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

25
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

26
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 1=

27
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:27,940
=The Double Game=

28
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:34,860
(Self-media blogger Wen Yan,
3 hours ago)

29
00:02:34,890 --> 00:02:35,730
Qing,

30
00:02:35,740 --> 00:02:36,580
I'm in.

31
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:38,560
No wonder you became a mega influencer.

32
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,343
You even got

33
00:02:39,354 --> 00:02:40,650
into a tight Luzhou Group gala.

34
00:02:40,650 --> 00:02:41,490
Stay safe.

35
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:42,340
Don't worry.

36
00:02:42,340 --> 00:02:43,280
I've got the target.

37
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:45,680
Once I get the evidence
of their illegal fundraising,

38
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:46,750
I'll be

39
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,150
the top influencer.

40
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:50,470
Ladies and gentlemen,

41
00:02:50,706 --> 00:02:53,000
(Lu Jianchuan, Chairman)
tonight isn't just a celebration

42
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:55,710
about the launch
of the Lianxin Island project,

43
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,150
one of our key projects.

44
00:02:58,590 --> 00:03:00,280
I'd also like to welcome my eldest son,

45
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,520
Lu Tingxiao.

46
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,840
He's back after years overseas.

47
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:08,400
Today, he'll officially take over
as CEO.

48
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:23,100
(CEO of Luzhou Group, Lu Tingxiao)

49
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,030
He's taking over the family business.

50
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:27,630
It looks like my target

51
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,630
is Lu Tingxiao now.

52
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:32,610
Lin Zhi'er,

53
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:33,590
where were you?

54
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:34,840
(Lin Zhi'er?)

55
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:36,300
Tingxiao's out of wine.

56
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:38,380
(Xu Shulin, stepmother)
Get him a fresh glass.

57
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,400
What a talented young man.

58
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:43,240
Be smart about this.

59
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:45,280
Go propose a toast to him.

60
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,000
(A toast?)

61
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,870
(Isn't this my chance?)

62
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,840
Okay.

63
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:56,630
(Lu Tingxiao,)

64
00:03:57,470 --> 00:04:00,560
(you're my target today.)

65
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,160
(Those drinks were tampered with.)

66
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:20,870
(That woman drugged us.)

67
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,560
Where's my brooch?

68
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,120
Are you looking for this?

69
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,430
A hidden camera.

70
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,270
Secret recording.

71
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,360
Did Xu Shulin send you?

72
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:57,680
Setting me up.

73
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,160
Turning it into a scandal.

74
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,270
That's exactly her style.

75
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:03,000
I don't know any Xu Shulin.

76
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,000
Give it back to me.

77
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,040
What's wrong with you?

78
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,310
How much did Xu Shulin pay you?

79
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,160
I'll pay double.

80
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:14,240
You won't be doing this for nothing.

81
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:16,750
Watch your mouth. I didn't film you.

82
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:17,960
I...

83
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,413
Hello?

84
00:05:22,424 --> 00:05:24,137
Are you the owner
of the yellow motorcycle?

85
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,630
Please come down and move it.

86
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:26,680
Sure, on my way.

87
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,430
There isn't a single car here.

88
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,800
Who called me?

89
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,600
(Where am I?)

90
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,080
(This is...)

91
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,110
(the Lu residence.)

92
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:43,270
(It's her.)

93
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,270
(She knocked me out.)

94
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:52,600
(She looks so much like me.)

95
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,360
(So,)

96
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,800
(she's a daughter-in-law here.)

97
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:59,800
(The mother-in-law drugged the wine)

98
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,510
(to set up the elder son
and his sister-in-law?)

99
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,000
Last night,

100
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,720
someone drugged me.

101
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,430
You must be behind it.

102
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,400
Tingxiao,

103
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,680
you can't say that without proof.

104
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,160
Don't pin that on me.

105
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,750
So, you won't admit it.

106
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,040
What do I need to admit?

107
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,310
I never did anything like that.

108
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,200
Zhi'er,

109
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,600
tell Tingxiao.

110
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,870
How could I ever hurt him?

111
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,560
You won't even answer me now?

112
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,190
Do I need Tingxiao to call you?

113
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:33,910
Tingxiao,

114
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:35,560
this is Tingyu's wife,

115
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,640
Lin Zhi'er.

116
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,800
(They really think I'm Lin Zhi'er now.)

117
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,600
(Should I play along?)

118
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:41,670
Greet him.

119
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:43,390
(Greet him?)

120
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:45,190
(This is so awkward.)

121
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,200
Go on.

122
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,040
Hurry up.

123
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,270
Tingxiao.

124
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,160
(Oh, my god.)

125
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:05,790
(She's...)

126
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:07,830
(my sister-in-law?)

127
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,950
(Xu Shulin,)

128
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,560
(for your son,)

129
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,750
(you'd do anything shameful.)

130
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,510
(And Lin Zhi'er too.)

131
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:31,670
Mr. Lu,

132
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,440
we found Xu Wangzu, Xu Shulin's brother,

133
00:08:33,550 --> 00:08:34,600
lining his own pockets.

134
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:37,080
He used Luzhou Group funds for futures.

135
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,000
Find a major media outlet.

136
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:41,360
Get this story out.

137
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,270
Xu Shulin's had it too easy

138
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:45,670
all these years.

139
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:47,630
It's time to end it.

140
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,800
You're back.

141
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,320
Aunt Hui.

142
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,550
Have you eaten yet?

143
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:57,870
Not yet.

144
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:58,870
I'll cook for you.

145
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,840
Alright.

146
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:13,300
(Jin Chanchan Studio)

147
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:19,270
Sis, you're finally back.

148
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:20,230
Come take a look.

149
00:09:20,910 --> 00:09:21,750
This month,

150
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,630
that pool hall video blew up again.

151
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,870
Today, you're the target.

152
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,120
If I'm calling you out,

153
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:28,510
why wait?

154
00:09:28,636 --> 00:09:30,483
(Coaching or a trap?)
The Feis' Billiards Club

155
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,630
looks like coaching.

156
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:33,360
But it's hiding a mess.

157
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:34,590
Look at these views.

158
00:09:34,633 --> 00:09:35,586
(Qing, assistant)
Look.

159
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:37,480
Our KPI is solid again this month.

160
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,200
Not bad.

161
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:40,960
One more good deed.

162
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:43,000
But I've heard

163
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,480
(Very deep)
the boss, Fei Yifan,

164
00:09:44,630 --> 00:09:45,870
(Wear a dive suit)
is mad.

165
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:46,910
That's the point.

166
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,030
The more mad he is,

167
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:50,510
the more it shows we hit his sore spot.

168
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:52,870
Enough about that.

169
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,720
Let's handle
the Lianxin Island deal first.

170
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,380
I'm going to meet a tipster.

171
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,960
He has inside info on Luzhou Group.

172
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,630
(Why is he here?)

173
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,840
You think a mask hides you from me?

174
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,790
You're everywhere, Zhi'er.

175
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:41,510
Tingxiao,

176
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,680
what a coincidence.

177
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,320
Coincidence?

178
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:46,630
Didn't you follow me here?

179
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,790
Me? Following you?

180
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,910
I got here first.

181
00:10:51,683 --> 00:10:52,740
What did Xu Shulin tell you

182
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,040
to do to set me up?

183
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:55,750
I came on my own.

184
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,150
I've got things to do.

185
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:02,440
Did you

186
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:03,630
follow me here?

187
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:05,440
This is too coincidental.

188
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,670
I'm meeting someone here.

189
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,910
You're meeting someone?

190
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,000
At a bar?

191
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:17,990
A woman?

192
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,840
Do I need to report that to you?

193
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,280
What do you want?

194
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,870
You're here to have fun.

195
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,240
I'm here to work.

196
00:11:25,366 --> 00:11:26,320
That makes me above you.

197
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:27,960
Work?

198
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:32,390
Here?

199
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,800
So what?

200
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,440
My work is flexible.

201
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,370
I can do it anywhere.

202
00:11:36,390 --> 00:11:37,360
I'm not picky at all.

203
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:38,600
I never complain.

204
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:40,600
Top-notch skills, great attitude.

205
00:11:40,790 --> 00:11:43,150
I'm a top star in the business.

206
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,550
Top star?

207
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,390
So, this is what you do in secret.

208
00:11:47,770 --> 00:11:48,650
So what?

209
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,790
I love what I do.

210
00:11:49,890 --> 00:11:50,730
I get it right

211
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:51,590
every single time.

212
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:52,870
A lot of people come to me.

213
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,080
But my energy is limited.

214
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,600
I only take

215
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,800
the intense

216
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,200
and thrilling ones.

217
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,720
Intense

218
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,680
and thrilling?

219
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:06,200
After all, I care about depth.

220
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,360
You really have no sense of shame.

221
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,720
Shame?

222
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:16,510
I'm a little angel for justice.

223
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:17,790
How am I shameless?

224
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:23,200
(Quite the top star,)

225
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,800
(Lin Zhi'er.)

226
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:34,910
Where's Jin Chanchan?

227
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,630
She should be there.

228
00:12:36,810 --> 00:12:37,790
I'll contact her again.

229
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,600
Send me her phone number.

230
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:40,960
Yes.

231
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,390
Who? Spit it out.

232
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:55,150
Do you know how late you are?

233
00:12:55,870 --> 00:12:56,710
Jin Chanchan,

234
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,360
is this your work standard?

235
00:12:58,790 --> 00:12:59,840
I'm informing you now:

236
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,270
This deal is off.

237
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,550
What is your problem?

238
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:05,030
You stood me up.

239
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:06,320
How can you say that?

240
00:13:06,410 --> 00:13:07,250
I'm telling you.

241
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:08,960
I don't even want this deal anymore.

242
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,040
You...

243
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,200
Say that again.

244
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:20,030
What's wrong with you?

245
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,120
I'll say this once more.

246
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,320
I don't want your deal anymore.

247
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,030
How interesting,

248
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,270
Lin Zhi'er.

249
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,000
Tingxiao.

250
00:14:02,630 --> 00:14:04,080
♪This door♪

251
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:09,230
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

252
00:14:09,710 --> 00:14:13,270
♪With a voice even lighter♪

253
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:16,080
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

254
00:14:16,530 --> 00:14:17,900
♪I know now♪

255
00:14:18,230 --> 00:14:23,110
♪What the chill in my body means♪

256
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:26,330
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

257
00:14:26,530 --> 00:14:29,950
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

258
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:33,110
♪To complete♪

259
00:14:33,570 --> 00:14:37,320
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

260
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:39,960
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

261
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:43,650
♪Like a door with no key♪

262
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:46,280
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

263
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:49,860
♪The tears in my eyes♪

264
00:14:50,570 --> 00:14:53,120
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

265
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,860
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

266
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:57,700
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

267
00:14:57,910 --> 00:15:00,000
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

268
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:04,480
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

269
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:07,150
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

270
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:11,820
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
